{"type":null,"faqId":41627,"title":"Why does the touch screen respond slowly or isn't very responsive when using magnification gestures?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>After enabling magnification gestures, touching the screen three times will zoom in or out on the screen to make the content easier to see. Presently, this function is not designed in a way that fully matches common user habits, so, when using it, the touch screen may seem unresponsive.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>To turn off magnification gestures, go to </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Accessibility</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Magnification gestures </span><span>and turn off the </span><span class=\"s1\">Magnification gestures</span><span> switch.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140229\" style=\"width:2.1840277in;height:3.8868055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140230\" style=\"width:2.1881945in;height:3.8909721in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140231\" style=\"width:2.1840277in;height:3.8868055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0006198753\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0006198754\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947950\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947951\"><a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005947952\"></a></a></a></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=140232\" style=\"width:0.59375in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>The figures are for your reference only. The actual screens may vary.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"7087","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442207708000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-L01","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"RIO-L01, G7 plus","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}